            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"世界黃金協會稱金價難估頂\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nf1Up7kS55CofpaLALYkSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/61823090-fbe5-11f0-b5bf-2f567292e57a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">世界黃金協會稱金價難估頂</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
