        {
            "title": "特朗普風輕雲淡 歐元兌美元漲破1.20大關",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國總統特朗普稱自己並不擔心本幣的跌勢後，歐元兌美元自2021年6月以來首次升至1.20上方。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐元升幅擴大，兌美元一度大漲1.7%至1.2081。美元則對十國集團所有主要對手貨幣回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期權市場對歐元的看漲情緒依然高漲。對沖或押注未來一年歐元兌美元走強的溢價相較於貶值的押注本周上升到了2020年3月以來的最高水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HDohPOYgEmZnGemo.hkJuw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/027e17f4cdc6778404ed49fdafcc3ff6\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場對美國赤字不斷擴大和貿易摩擦加劇的擔憂給美元帶來了廣泛的壓力。此外，投資者面對地緣政治風險日益上升加速將資金分散至黃​​金和其它儲備資產。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-74c0c142-825f-35bf-bacb-c0890a9a6284-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者當前將密切關注外匯市場對聯儲會周三利率決策的反應。互換交易員預計本周美國央行將按兵不動，消化的年內降息幅度略低於兩次、每次下調25個基點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">同時，美國政府再次停擺的威脅也加劇了美元的壓力。參議院民主黨領袖查克·舒默表示，除非共和黨剝離對國土安全部的撥款否則將阻止本周的支出法案，從而增加了聯邦政府部分停擺的概率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Euro Rallies Above $1.20 on Broad Dollar Weakness, Trump Remarks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Carter Johnson.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E9%A2%A8%E8%BC%95%E9%9B%B2%E6%B7%A1-%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%85%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%BC%B2%E7%A0%B41-20%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%9C-221311559.html",
